data.description: SOLAR ENERGY SAVINGS!!! Oversized corner lot home with 3 sides brick, 4 bedrooms upstairs, 2 1/2 bathrooms with new interior paint throughout the home and exterior painting. The open floorplan is perfect for entertaining. Cozy up next to the fireplace in the family room with beautiful wood floors. The huge backyard provides plentiful space for a pool. Primary suite up with dual vanities, barn doors, and a nice upgraded shower stall. The bonus room upstairs was converted to a 4th bedroom with a closet and barn doors. The paid for solar panels will help with your utilities. Don't miss the opportunity to make this delightful residence your new home! Conveniently located near UTSA, USAA, the Medical Center, La Cantera, SeaWorld, Six Flags, and more!
